title: NFL Combine Winners and Losers, Franchise Tags (Football 3/2)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Joel Corry and John Breech to talk about the franchise tag situations around the NFL and then Brinson, Breech and Ryan Wilson break down Kyler Murray's performance on the podium and discuss other winners and losers from the second day of the combine.
